=\"services\" class=\"container\">    \n<div class=\"row\">\n    <div class=\"col-sm-9\"><br>\n      \n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"methodText\">The Enterprise Cloud is no more a cost reducer, today it is a business differentiator that enables innovation and growth. <strong>Microsoft’s cloud solution, Azure</strong> is enabling organizations of all sizes to get to the cloud quicker with maximum affordability and flexibility. The Azure platform is used to deliver superior performance while helping to control costs. Microsoft Azure can extend your infrastructure and provides scalable, durable cloud storage, backup and recovery solutions for any data, big and small.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"aaa.png\">\n\t\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"methodText\">Miracle delivers innovative public, private and hybrid cloud integration services with deep technical expertise that supports you and your solutions. Our team will help assess your needs and recommend the best cloud strategy for your needs. To </p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"heavy\">Microsoft Cloud Offerings by Miracle</h1>\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t    <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t        <h3 class=\"heavy\"></h3>\n\t\t        <ul>\n\t\t            <li><strong>Cloud Strategy and Planning Services (Public, Private, or Hybrid)</strong></li>\n\t\t            <li><strong>Cloud Migration Services – On-Prem to Cloud</strong></li>\n\t\t            <li><strong>Cloud Preparation/Remediation/Migration Services for:</strong></li>\n\t\t            <ul>\n\t\t            <li>Office 365 (SharePoint, Skype/Lync, Office)</li>\n\t\t            <li>Microsoft Azure</li>\n\t\t            <ul>\n\t\t            <li>Azure Stack</li>\n\t\t            <li>Web App Services</li>\n\t\t            <li>Mobile App Services</li>\n\t\t            <li>API App Service and Logic App Services</li>\n\t\t            <li>Azure SQL Services</li>\n\t\t            </ul>\n\t\t            \n\t\t            <li>Dynamics CRM Online</li></ul>\n\t\t            <li><strong>Azure Testing Services</strong></li>\n\t\t        </ul>\n\t\t    </div>\n\t\t     <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t          <h3 class=\"heavy\"></h3>\n\t\t        <ul>\n\t\t            <li><strong>Azure App Services – Architecture, Development & DevOps</strong></li>\n\t\t            <ul>\n\t\t            <li>Web App Services</li>\n\t\t            <li>Mobile App Services</li>\n\t\t            <li>API App Services</li>\n\t\t            <li>Logic App Services</li>\n\t\t         </ul>\n\t\t         <li><strong>Azure IoT  Suite – Design, Development and Implementation</strong></li>\n                    <li><strong>Business Intelligence – Azure SQL BI Stack and PowerBI</strong></li>\n                    <li><strong>Infrastructure Services – Managed/Support Services</strong></li>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li> DevOPS cycle, Monitoring and Administration</li>\n                        <li>Azure Operations Management Suite</li>\n                        <li>Powershell Scripting</li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <li><strong>DevOPS</strong> - TFS Online</li>\n\t\t        </ul>\n\t\t     </div>\n\t\t     <p class=\"methodText\">For more information regarding our Microsoft Cloud, IoT and DevOps Offerings, reach out to us at <a href=\"mailto:microsoft@miraclesoft.com\"><strong>microsoft@miraclesoft.com.</strong></a> </p>\n\t\t     \n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t\t<br><br>\n     </div> \n\t<div class=\"col-sm-3 sidebar pull-right\">\n            <br>\n \n           \n            <div class=\"list-group\" id=\"MainMenu\">\n                <div class=\"list-group panel\">\n               <style type=\"text/css\">\n                  .list-group-item-1 {\n                  position: relative;\n                  display: block;\n                  padding: 10px 15px;\n                  margin-bottom: -1px;\n                 \n                  }\n                  .btn-primary {\n               